WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:11.590 --> 02:12.424
Hey, Mickey.

02:16.928 --> 02:19.347
- Don't tell Mom.
- Don't tell me what?

02:19.598 --> 02:22.225
Nothing. I forgot to go
to the store. No milk.

02:23.351 --> 02:24.853
Fresh one down in the fridge.

02:26.021 --> 02:27.314
What's that you got
behind your back?

02:27.522 --> 02:28.774
Mom, you should've
seen his face.

02:28.982 --> 02:30.484
You're a pushover, young man.

03:38.760 --> 03:41.263
- Good morning, sir.
- Hey, Ben.

03:42.514 --> 03:43.640
- Sit down.
- Sure.

03:45.684 --> 03:47.436
- How do you feel?
- Good.

03:47.644 --> 03:50.397
- Did you swim this morning?
- Yeah.

03:51.982 --> 03:53.275
What are your holding
for your hundreds?

03:53.900 --> 03:55.277
Fifty plus on the minute-thirty.

03:56.445 --> 03:57.362
Not bad.

03:57.571 --> 03:59.322
I can get it under 45, I think.

03:59.781 --> 04:03.118
Can you do it in time
for the Fillmore meet?

04:03.326 --> 04:03.952
Why?

04:05.370 --> 04:07.664
Stanford scouts are flying down.

04:09.833 --> 04:12.210
For the next 8 days,
I want you living in that pool.

04:12.544 --> 04:15.338
And when you're not swimming,
I want you thinking about it.

04:15.589 --> 04:17.048
I want you dreaming about it.

04:17.466 --> 04:19.593
- You hear me?
- Yeah.

04:19.885 --> 04:23.180
I don't mean to put any
undue pressure on you.

04:24.598 --> 04:26.850
What are we talking about here,
your entire future?

04:27.100 --> 04:29.394
Right. Right.

04:30.020 --> 04:30.937
Go and change.

04:31.146 --> 04:32.397
Alright. Thank you.

04:36.485 --> 04:39.863
California boy, can I
have your autograph?

04:40.071 --> 04:40.697
Nasty.

04:41.198 --> 04:42.574
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

04:43.492 --> 04:45.494
- Nervous?
- Yeah, a little bit.

04:45.827 --> 04:47.579
- You're gonna kick ass.
- I hope so.

04:47.788 --> 04:50.207
That is, until I outswim
your little punk ass.

04:50.457 --> 04:53.293
And those scouts forget your name
and grant me the scholarship.

04:53.502 --> 04:54.795
I just remembered why
we broke up, Josh.

04:55.003 --> 04:56.046
You couldn't handle me in bed.

04:56.254 --> 04:58.215
No, because you're an asshole.

04:59.007 --> 05:01.426
Ben just got good news.
The response is congratulations.

05:01.635 --> 05:02.761
You're right.

05:04.387 --> 05:05.680
Congratulations, dickhead.

05:06.306 --> 05:09.434
- Let's not be mature today.
- I'm all for that.

05:09.643 --> 05:12.646
Let's make it Opposite Day
and everybody be immature.

05:22.614 --> 05:24.032
Hey, watch it!

05:28.620 --> 05:29.913
Forget about it.

05:30.205 --> 05:31.248
Hey, Dante.

05:34.209 --> 05:36.837
He's crazy. He's a freak.

05:38.880 --> 05:40.674
- Hey, congrats.
- Thanks.

05:45.053 --> 05:46.430
- So...
- So?

05:49.224 --> 05:51.017
It might actually happen?

05:51.476 --> 05:54.938
Can you picture it?
Me in California?

05:55.814 --> 05:58.692
- And me in Rhode Island.
- Yeah.

06:02.320 --> 06:05.949
- That's 3,000 miles.
- I know how many miles it is.

06:07.242 --> 06:09.035
- I love you.
- I love you too.

06:11.288 --> 06:13.415
Nothing is going to change that.

06:16.752 --> 06:20.714
- I bought you something.
- What?

06:23.383 --> 06:24.760
Open it first.

06:28.221 --> 06:31.433
- That is so beautiful.
- You're beautiful.

06:31.933 --> 06:34.186
- You're so beautiful.
- Thank you.

06:35.437 --> 06:39.024
I would even be here if it
wasn't for you believing in me.

06:42.444 --> 06:43.987
This is a ploy to get laid.

06:45.030 --> 06:45.864
Is it working?

07:14.476 --> 07:15.519
Excuse me?

07:17.979 --> 07:21.274
I can't get this thing open
and I'm late for English.

07:22.025 --> 07:22.901
Do you think you could...?

07:23.693 --> 07:25.987
I can take a look, yeah.

07:28.115 --> 07:29.950
They gave me the combination, but...

07:30.325 --> 07:31.993
I don't need it. I just need...

07:34.746 --> 07:36.498
...that, right there.
- This?

07:39.000 --> 07:39.626
Thank you.

07:41.586 --> 07:43.380
Can't let you be late
on your first day.

07:43.839 --> 07:45.132
Is it that obvious?

08:00.105 --> 08:01.773
Thank you so much.

08:02.274 --> 08:04.901
- Here.
- Keep it.

08:06.319 --> 08:08.280
You never know when
I might need saving again.

08:09.698 --> 08:11.867
I'm Madison Bell.

08:12.075 --> 08:12.951
Ben Cronin. Hi.

08:14.035 --> 08:15.495
What the letter for, Ben Cronin?

08:15.996 --> 08:17.831
The letter is for swimming,
Madison Bell.

08:18.874 --> 08:22.085
- Are you good?
- I'm okay, yeah.

08:27.174 --> 08:27.799
See you around.

08:28.008 --> 08:29.426
- See you.
- Bye.

08:38.769 --> 08:41.645
- There's my swim champ.
- Mom...

08:43.774 --> 08:46.568
Better get started with Mr. Tillman.
He's been asking for you.

08:53.408 --> 08:56.411
Ben! Give me some good news.

08:56.620 --> 08:57.996
Scouts are coming next week.

08:58.205 --> 08:59.122
Girl Scouts?

08:59.456 --> 09:02.501
No, swim scouts, from Stanford,
to see me.

09:02.709 --> 09:04.127
I asked you to find me a woman.

09:04.336 --> 09:06.963
It's hard to find anyone in
your age bracket still breathing.

09:07.339 --> 09:08.173
Here you go.

09:10.842 --> 09:11.885
I almost forgot...

09:14.554 --> 09:16.807
That's my boy!

09:20.936 --> 09:22.521
Anything else?

09:25.190 --> 09:26.608
You guys okay?

09:35.033 --> 09:37.953
- Did you miss me?
- Like crazy.

09:38.870 --> 09:41.498
Wait. I've been thinking.

09:42.874 --> 09:44.835
What if I didn't go to
Rhode Island next year?

09:45.293 --> 09:45.919
What do you mean?

09:46.211 --> 09:49.047
What if I went to Berkeley instead?

09:50.006 --> 09:52.634
We'd be closer when you
go to Stanford and...

09:53.427 --> 09:55.804
- We could get an apartment.
- Amy.

09:56.596 --> 09:59.141
- I haven't gotten in yet.
- But you will.

10:02.561 --> 10:04.271
If you hate the idea, it's okay.

10:04.729 --> 10:08.024
No, are you kidding?
It's a great idea.

10:08.650 --> 10:11.278
- Really?
- Really. It's a great idea.

10:24.875 --> 10:26.001
Morning, Benjamin.

10:28.670 --> 10:31.047
- A little early for you, isn't it?
- Yes, it is.

10:31.715 --> 10:35.010
I thought I'd get a little
lane time in before the rush.

10:37.012 --> 10:38.513
Got to look good for the scouts.

10:39.222 --> 10:40.182
Yeah, right.

10:40.599 --> 10:44.728
I know they'll be looking at you,

10:46.188 --> 10:47.981
but the rest of us
will be in the pool.

10:48.523 --> 10:51.026
The more the merrier, buddy.

10:52.527 --> 10:56.406
So... Madison Bell.

10:58.241 --> 10:58.867
What?

11:00.243 --> 11:03.538
She's a senior, originally
from down South.

11:03.747 --> 11:07.459
I plan to hear that Southern accent
when she moans my name.

11:07.667 --> 11:09.211
Or when she applies
the restraining order.

11:10.128 --> 11:12.297
- Do you want to hear or not?
- Sure. What's up?

11:12.631 --> 11:16.676
The reason she's up here
is her family's in Europe.

11:17.469 --> 11:21.139
She's staying here with her cousin.
Guess who her cousin is.

11:21.348 --> 11:23.975
- Who is her cousin?
- Christopher Dante.

11:26.645 --> 11:30.607
You're set. He loves you.
He's gonna put in a good word.

11:30.816 --> 11:34.319
- Do you think he would, seriously?
- He really would.

11:34.569 --> 11:36.780
- Think about it.
- No! No!

11:55.340 --> 11:56.299
Shit!

11:59.261 --> 12:00.262
I'm sorry. Are you okay?

12:00.470 --> 12:01.763
- I'm fine.
- Are you sure?

12:02.097 --> 12:03.557
- No, don't worry about it.
- I didn't see you.

12:03.765 --> 12:05.934
- Really, it's all right.
- Here, here.

12:06.601 --> 12:08.437
Thanks. It's okay.

12:09.062 --> 12:11.064
- Let me give you a ride.
- No, I'm fine.

12:11.273 --> 12:13.150
It's the least I can do.

12:13.358 --> 12:16.111
- I'm fine.
- Please? I insist.

12:18.905 --> 12:22.200
- Well, if you insist.
- I do. Come on.

12:24.786 --> 12:29.416
I wasn't looking at the road.
I thought I saw somebody I knew.

12:43.180 --> 12:43.805
That way?

12:59.070 --> 13:00.363
How's that for service?

13:01.406 --> 13:03.241
You're a handy guy to have around.

13:03.533 --> 13:05.494
Yeah, handy all over the place.

13:09.081 --> 13:10.082
See you at school.

13:12.334 --> 13:14.086
See you at school.

13:16.004 --> 13:18.882
Handy all over the place.
What is that?

14:43.175 --> 14:44.468
It's a boy.

14:49.514 --> 14:50.140
Hello?

14:50.682 --> 14:53.477
Hi, Madison. This is Ben Cronin.

14:55.645 --> 14:57.147
You left your notebook in my car.

14:59.733 --> 15:01.026
Pretty sharp. Got a date?

15:02.194 --> 15:05.781
It's just pants and a shirt.
I'll be back in half an hour.

15:26.510 --> 15:27.094
How's it going?

15:28.428 --> 15:30.388
You don't have to be nice to me.

15:30.597 --> 15:32.140
She's already going out with you.

15:32.349 --> 15:35.060
No, we're not going out.
I'm just returning her notebook.

15:35.602 --> 15:38.688
I'll take it.
No reason to hold you up.

15:38.939 --> 15:40.649
I'm sure you've got
more important things to do.

15:42.067 --> 15:42.901
Christopher?

15:45.487 --> 15:47.072
Why didn't you tell me
I had a visitor?

16:11.763 --> 16:14.391
I had to get out of there.
It's so stifling.

16:15.434 --> 16:16.476
You okay?

16:16.685 --> 16:21.106
Yeah. I haven't really
eaten all day.

16:25.902 --> 16:27.654
- Here's your order.
- Thank you.

16:27.863 --> 16:28.488
You're welcome.

16:28.697 --> 16:30.115
So, I've been dying to know...

16:30.323 --> 16:33.535
How come a nice boy like you knows
how to break into girls' lockers?

16:33.910 --> 16:35.746
I didn't used to be so nice.

16:36.413 --> 16:37.539
That's hard to believe.

16:37.748 --> 16:41.042
It was a long time ago.
Everybody's forgotten about it,

16:41.251 --> 16:42.836
except the cops.

16:43.086 --> 16:44.379
You don't have to tell me.

16:44.588 --> 16:47.674
No, I had a situation
with drugs which

16:48.425 --> 16:50.051
turned into a situation
with stealing.

16:50.510 --> 16:53.346
I spent 6 months in juvenile hall.

16:53.555 --> 16:55.265
It was the best thing
that's ever happened to me

16:55.557 --> 16:56.475
'cause they had a pool.

16:57.267 --> 17:01.229
This shitty lab pool that
hadn't been used in years

17:01.438 --> 17:03.523
and I got assigned to clean it.

17:04.523 --> 17:06.943
Soon I was swimming in it
more than I was cleaning it.

17:07.194 --> 17:09.695
It was easier for me to
jump in the pool and forget about

17:10.113 --> 17:14.576
all the mess going on around me
and just swim.

17:15.117 --> 17:19.455
When I play music sometimes,
I just play cello,

17:19.790 --> 17:23.877
and I float out of my body,
above the music where no one

17:25.087 --> 17:26.213
can touch me,

17:26.797 --> 17:28.757
hurt me...

17:28.965 --> 17:30.258
I can escape.

17:31.968 --> 17:33.386
Do you want to escape?

17:33.970 --> 17:37.265
Yeah, sometimes.

17:39.309 --> 17:40.602
But not right now.

17:41.561 --> 17:43.146
Right now, I like where I am.

17:51.196 --> 17:52.739
I should tell you something.

17:52.989 --> 17:56.952
- You have a girlfriend.
- Yeah. Amy.

17:57.411 --> 18:01.373
- Is it serious?
- Yeah, it is.

18:03.083 --> 18:06.878
She's the other reason
I turned my life around.

18:08.505 --> 18:10.006
Story of my life.

18:10.757 --> 18:14.344
Can't expect the nicest,
most handsome guy to be single too.

18:16.596 --> 18:19.599
Don't worry about me.
I got someone waiting in New York.

18:20.684 --> 18:23.812
A great guy.
A really good shortstop too.

18:24.020 --> 18:25.439
The Mets are pretty interested.

18:25.647 --> 18:27.107
The Mets? Really?

18:27.315 --> 18:28.150
- Yeah.
- Wow!

18:28.942 --> 18:31.111
But until we can live
in the same place,

18:31.570 --> 18:33.321
we agreed to see other people

18:33.864 --> 18:35.449
and that's what I intend to do.

18:36.575 --> 18:38.535
My friend Josh

18:39.077 --> 18:42.539
would murder me and step over
my dead body to be here with you.

18:44.207 --> 18:46.501
Thanks, I'm not interested in Josh.

18:56.344 --> 18:57.721
I should take you home.

18:58.388 --> 19:01.099
- Yeah, you should.
- Yeah.

19:03.477 --> 19:05.020
But...

19:07.647 --> 19:09.232
I'm not ready to say goodnight.

19:12.527 --> 19:13.487
What do you want to do?

20:03.954 --> 20:06.248
Careful. I can't swim.

20:06.790 --> 20:08.250
- Really?
- Yeah.

20:09.167 --> 20:10.001
Show me how?

20:12.587 --> 20:13.422
Yeah.

20:16.883 --> 20:18.760
Come here.

20:22.305 --> 20:23.598
You got to know how to float

20:24.474 --> 20:27.561
and kick, so lean back.

20:27.936 --> 20:29.896
Yeah... very important.

20:30.105 --> 20:32.065
You're a natural.

20:34.192 --> 20:35.485
- Like that?
- Yeah.

20:42.242 --> 20:43.535
The side's right here.

20:49.916 --> 20:51.042
That's easy.

21:10.020 --> 21:11.772
It's okay. I want you to.

21:22.949 --> 21:26.912
Wait, wait.
We can't do this.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.413
We can't do this.

21:28.622 --> 21:31.541
It's all right.
It'll be our little secret.

21:35.337 --> 21:37.297
Maybe not so little.

22:09.913 --> 22:11.206
Ben!

22:12.582 --> 22:13.875
Tell me you love me.

22:16.336 --> 22:17.254
What?

22:17.462 --> 22:21.091
You don't have to mean it.
Just say it for me.

22:26.346 --> 22:27.639
I love you.

22:48.201 --> 22:49.035
So...

22:53.707 --> 22:54.541
So...

22:58.587 --> 23:00.964
- Don't think I do this all the time.
- No!

23:01.840 --> 23:04.676
Of course not, no.

23:06.219 --> 23:09.264
I don't want to be
a locker room joke, so...

23:11.516 --> 23:12.809
don't tell anybody, okay?

23:16.396 --> 23:17.898
I won't tell anybody.

23:19.065 --> 23:22.944
Good. Still friends?

23:34.581 --> 23:35.665
See you tomorrow.

24:15.372 --> 24:17.457
You are so busted.

24:19.876 --> 24:22.712
I thought you'd keep me company
in the restaurant last night.

24:23.130 --> 24:26.925
I'm sorry. I had some homework
at Randy's.

24:27.509 --> 24:28.802
How's his mom doing?

24:31.054 --> 24:33.014
She broke her wrist.
Is it still in a cast?

24:34.474 --> 24:37.227
She seemed okay.
I'm trying to...

24:37.894 --> 24:40.772
Didn't seem like she was in pain.

24:40.981 --> 24:42.524
That's good.

24:42.983 --> 24:45.610
- I left you something.
- What?

24:46.153 --> 24:47.654
It's in your locker.

24:48.405 --> 24:49.990
I hope you like it.

24:50.198 --> 24:52.534
- I love you.
- Yeah, I love you too.

25:17.851 --> 25:21.480
Ben, I'm so proud of you.
I love having you in my life.

25:21.688 --> 25:24.191
- Where will your parents be?
- Jamaica.

25:24.733 --> 25:27.778
- Will they be gone all weekend?
- No, all week.

25:28.862 --> 25:29.988
Nice.

25:30.322 --> 25:32.407
I didn't hear Amy invite you.

25:32.949 --> 25:34.576
I'm sorry, I didn't hear anyone
talking to you.

25:36.036 --> 25:37.996
Good time on the over-sleep.

25:38.205 --> 25:39.915
Coach is seriously pissed.

25:43.043 --> 25:44.169
Are these for me?

25:47.297 --> 25:50.175
They're a thank you for the card.

25:50.383 --> 25:51.426
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

26:16.076 --> 26:17.452
Way to swim, Josh!

26:18.245 --> 26:21.373
Everybody else, keep your focus.

26:21.957 --> 26:24.584
Focus is key.

26:27.045 --> 26:29.172
Are you okay? What's up?

26:38.598 --> 26:43.103
I don't know if it's
this low-carb diet I'm on,

26:43.645 --> 26:46.273
but Ben and I are like this now
in the water.

26:46.481 --> 26:49.317
Josh, he had a bad swim.
Why don't you give it a rest?

26:49.651 --> 26:50.652
What's up, ladies?

26:51.403 --> 26:54.156
What's going on? Everything cool?

26:54.781 --> 26:57.075
- My swimming buddy.
- That's right.

26:57.284 --> 26:59.453
- May the best man win.
- Absolutely.

26:59.661 --> 27:01.329
There you go. I'm sorry.

27:01.538 --> 27:02.622
Let me give you mine, buddy.

27:12.007 --> 27:13.842
Ben, over here!

27:14.634 --> 27:15.927
Oh my gosh!

27:18.180 --> 27:21.016
I missed you. Where have you been?

27:21.224 --> 27:22.851
- Around.
- Yeah?

27:23.977 --> 27:26.021
Yeah. That's so great. Come here.

27:26.229 --> 27:29.524
There's someone I want you to meet.
Madison?

27:31.026 --> 27:32.778
This is my boyfriend, Ben Cronin.

27:34.112 --> 27:36.406
Nice to meet you. Madison Bell.

27:37.157 --> 27:38.033
Nice to meet you.

27:38.408 --> 27:40.952
I already know all about him.

27:41.369 --> 27:44.206
Amy can't stop talking about
her perfect boyfriend.

27:44.414 --> 27:46.124
Even when I beg her to stop.

27:50.754 --> 27:52.839
Excuse me. I gotta use the bathroom.

27:53.173 --> 27:53.882
You want to hold this?

27:54.091 --> 27:56.718
- It was nice meeting you.
- You too.

27:59.846 --> 28:03.809
Cronin, I'm making a video run
and you're truck's blocking me in.

28:04.434 --> 28:06.686
I'll do it. Just one second.

28:07.020 --> 28:08.021
I'll be right back.

28:08.355 --> 28:09.523
I gotta get more ice first.

28:10.107 --> 28:11.233
Keys?

28:11.441 --> 28:13.276
Yes.

28:22.786 --> 28:24.454
Don't we have English together?

28:52.190 --> 28:53.942
She's really nice.

28:55.694 --> 29:00.323
She's so sweet and uncomplicated.

29:00.866 --> 29:04.369
Madison, this is a little
awkward for me.

29:04.619 --> 29:05.912
We could go somewhere else.

29:07.205 --> 29:09.624
- Not what I meant.
- I know. I'm kidding.

29:11.126 --> 29:13.587
Is it hot in here or is it me?

29:16.757 --> 29:20.385
I know you're tied up tonight,
but when do I see you again?

29:21.970 --> 29:24.598
- I don't know.
- How about tomorrow?

29:24.806 --> 29:27.976
Tomorrow's not good for me.

29:29.686 --> 29:32.105
I should get back to the party.

29:32.314 --> 29:35.525
By the way, do you have my panties?

29:35.734 --> 29:38.695
- Excuse me?
- My panties.

29:40.363 --> 29:42.449
I may have left them in your car.

29:57.547 --> 29:59.758
Let me do it. It's acting funny.

30:02.511 --> 30:03.261
Thank you.

31:57.375 --> 31:58.877
You got to bring your times down.

31:59.711 --> 32:01.671
I'm not seeing Olympic swimming.

32:02.714 --> 32:04.257
And neither will Stanford.

32:06.468 --> 32:07.761
I know. I've got a lot on my mind.

32:09.971 --> 32:10.680
Sorry.

32:15.727 --> 32:17.145
Get your head back in the game.

32:18.146 --> 32:19.523
- Are you listening?
- Yeah.

32:21.441 --> 32:22.067
Sorry.

32:22.442 --> 32:24.694
If you think you'll waltz it through...

32:24.945 --> 32:26.238
No, Coach, no!

32:28.323 --> 32:30.575
I'll be ready on Thursday.

32:33.245 --> 32:36.540
And whatever's going on
between you and your girl,

32:37.833 --> 32:38.458
fix it.

32:40.085 --> 32:41.044
Now go.

32:53.807 --> 32:57.102
- I'm home!
- We're in here.

32:58.353 --> 32:59.229
We?

33:03.650 --> 33:05.610
- He's so cute.
- Yes, I know.

33:05.819 --> 33:07.112
Happy birthday!

33:08.321 --> 33:10.574
