37:20.949 --> 37:24.703
Shit, Cronin. Get a grip.

37:33.962 --> 37:35.839
<i>Please enter your password. </i>

37:38.133 --> 37:40.677
<i>You have 81 new emails. </i>

37:50.729 --> 37:52.397
<i>Picture received. </i>

38:13.085 --> 38:13.960
Gotcha!

38:20.300 --> 38:22.719
So here's what I think.

38:23.095 --> 38:27.557
When school's over, we should
go to my empty, parentless house...

38:27.766 --> 38:29.559
I have work.

38:33.688 --> 38:34.815
Maybe afterwards.

38:35.982 --> 38:37.400
My shift starts at six.

38:38.944 --> 38:40.028
Tomorrow?

38:41.613 --> 38:42.906
Is it the meet?

38:44.032 --> 38:47.994
