38:58.046 --> 38:59.714
I'll let you get back to it.

39:08.640 --> 39:10.016
I'll give you a call.

39:57.481 --> 40:01.443
- I'm Randy, a friend of Josh.
- Right.

40:01.985 --> 40:04.321
- He's told me about you.
- Really?

40:04.529 --> 40:06.740
- Yeah, he did.
- Cool.

40:07.741 --> 40:08.909
Well, I'll see you.

40:12.204 --> 40:14.831
So you and Josh? That's cool.

40:28.678 --> 40:30.555
Could we just sit down?

40:34.184 --> 40:37.479
I want you to know that I know.

40:39.481 --> 40:42.901
- You know?
- I know how freaked out you are.

40:44.444 --> 40:47.280
I know why. It's because of
the other night, right?

40:49.616 --> 40:50.450
Yeah.

40:52.494 --> 40:54.746
