it's senior year.

40:55.080 --> 40:57.999
I was afraid of losing you, but...

40:58.208 --> 40:59.835
but we don't have to make plans now.

41:00.085 --> 41:04.047
We can take everything one step
at a time. I'm fine with that.

41:06.174 --> 41:07.467
I am.

41:09.344 --> 41:10.637
That was my whole speech.

41:10.846 --> 41:12.639
I practiced it and everything.

41:16.476 --> 41:17.769
I don't deserve you.

41:20.605 --> 41:23.817
- Thank you.
- It's true.

41:26.987 --> 41:29.197
I've been looking all over for you.

41:30.282 --> 41:31.867
What are you doing in here?

41:32.784 --> 41:34.953
