41:43.378 --> 41:45.505
He doesn't mean anything to me.

41:46.715 --> 41:48.550
When I'm with him,
I pretend it's you.

41:50.719 --> 41:52.012
Wow!

41:53.722 --> 41:56.057
Did I do something wrong? Talk to me.

41:56.266 --> 41:59.060
I have a lot going on right now.

42:01.354 --> 42:04.232
Maybe too much.

42:04.483 --> 42:09.112
What don't you get?
I'm trying to drop you.

42:14.242 --> 42:15.786
You don't mean that.

42:17.162 --> 42:20.791
I don't know any other way
but to just say it.

42:22.084 --> 42:26.713
I'm not with you.
I'm with Amy. Amy!

42:27.422 --> 42:31.009
I told you this. Remember?

42:34.971 --> 42:36.264
Sure I remember.

42:37.390 --> 42:40.352
But I also remember
you told me you loved me.

42:45.524 --> 42:46.817
