You're gonna stop calling me,

45:45.662 --> 45:48.290
you're gonna stop paging me.
You're gonna stop visiting me!

45:48.498 --> 45:49.124
Okay?

45:49.708 --> 45:54.129
If you see me in the hallway,
pass by like I don't exist.

45:54.963 --> 45:57.466
