46:29.414 --> 46:30.332
Okay. I can wait.

46:31.416 --> 46:33.376
I'm not done till one in the morning.

46:33.585 --> 46:36.004
- You have to rest for the meet.
- Screw the meet.

46:37.214 --> 46:38.507
What's wrong?

46:38.840 --> 46:40.133
We can't talk about it here.

46:41.927 --> 46:46.556
I can skip first period
and we'll go for a drive.

46:47.099 --> 46:49.434
- The morning, okay.
- All right.

46:49.643 --> 46:51.603
- I love you.
- I love you too.

48:44.424 --> 48:47.344
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

48:50.972 --> 48:52.599
Why?

49:58.290 --> 49:59.124
Excuse me?

50:32.407 --> 50:33.825
Are those the scouts?

50:37.496 --> 50:38.538
Good luck.

50:55.597 --> 50:58.725
- Ben?
- Yeah?

51:06.817 --> 51:09.444
You tested positive for steroids.

51:11.988 --> 51:13.281
- What?
- You heard me.

51:14.366 --> 51:18.328
Steroids are banned
at this school, Ben.

51:19.246 --> 51:23.625
Leave the pool area. Clean out
your locker. You're off the team.

51:23.834 --> 51:25.919
You can't do this to me!

51:27.421 --> 51:30.215
It's a mistake. I don't take steroids!

51:30.549 --> 51:31.258
I don't take...

51:33.385 --> 51:34.970
You did this to yourself.

51:36.138 --> 51:39.057
Now go pack and go home.

51:52.571 --> 51:55.574
Where is she? Where is she?

51:55.782 --> 51:57.242
Dude, you're losing it.

51:59.870 --> 52:00.746
You helped her.

52:03.582 --> 52:05.959
Screw you, Ben.

52:11.882 --> 52:15.594
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,
Ben Cronin has been disqualified. </i>

52:17.012 --> 52:19.639
<i>Ben Cronin will not compete
in this race. </i>

52:19.848 --> 52:20.682
Come on.

52:30.484 --> 52:33.445
<i>The winner is Josh Jefferson
in lane two! </i>

52:33.653 --> 52:37.032
<i>Time is 1:33:60</i>

52:44.456 --> 52:45.582
Are you taking drugs again?

52:47.793 --> 52:49.377
Would you believe me
if I said no?

52:50.045 --> 52:52.172
This is how it started the last time.

52:53.256 --> 52:55.884
The lying, the screwing up
in school.

52:56.093 --> 52:57.677
Once guilty, always guilty, right?

53:00.347 --> 53:03.266
What I need is for everybody
to just leave me alone

53:03.809 --> 53:05.769
while I figure out how to
get my life back.

53:20.700 --> 53:21.326
Amy?

53:31.628 --> 53:36.007
- Are you okay?
- No.

53:39.344 --> 53:43.598
- And you?
- No.

53:48.270 --> 53:50.647
- I can't believe that...
- She did it.

53:58.447 --> 54:00.240
I really think you should go.

54:23.305 --> 54:24.598
Ben.

54:27.476 --> 54:28.310
Ben?

54:35.650 --> 54:39.154
- What's the matter?
- My name is not Ben.

54:41.323 --> 54:45.368
I know that. Josh, come here.

54:48.872 --> 54:50.582
Josh? Josh.

54:52.084 --> 54:53.376
It's all true, isn't it?

54:55.045 --> 54:56.004
What?

54:57.506 --> 54:58.799
Ben was telling the truth.

55:00.634 --> 55:03.345
You want to hurt him because
he doesn't want you anymore.

55:04.096 --> 55:05.472
Don't say that.

55:07.474 --> 55:08.517
I should have known.

55:09.935 --> 55:11.478
Ben would never do steroids.

55:12.312 --> 55:13.188
He doesn't need them.

55:14.439 --> 55:15.941
God.

55:16.608 --> 55:18.568
You know what? Screw you!

55:19.069 --> 55:20.028
How about that?

55:21.780 --> 55:25.867
Josh, get back here!

55:26.451 --> 55:29.454
Josh, come here!

55:29.663 --> 55:30.956
Josh!

55:35.001 --> 55:38.755
<i>It's okay. I want you to. Touch me. </i>

55:39.506 --> 55:42.801
<i>Hold me. Actually, you can't escape. </i>

55:43.009 --> 55:44.302
<i>Tell me you love me. </i>

55:44.636 --> 55:46.138
<i>I have to tell you something. </i>

55:46.346 --> 55:47.764
<i>-Tell me you love me.
