apologize in person. How's that?

01:11:00.302 --> 01:11:01.595
Excuse me.

01:11:36.880 --> 01:11:38.381
Shit!

01:11:39.007 --> 01:11:40.717
Hey, watch the papers.

01:12:24.511 --> 01:12:25.804
<i>She's doing fine. </i>

01:12:27.055 --> 01:12:28.348
